{"tid":253861,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"卡巴斯基：遭WannaCry感染的電腦有98%是Windows 7","createTime":"2017-05-22T17:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T04:46:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"619d86d7d91c5bdc6d743e9a15fd3fb7f3d33596","tid":253861,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:33:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">根據該實驗室的統計數據，在被WannaCry感染的視窗作業系統中，64位元的Windows 7佔了60.35%，32位元的Windows 7佔了31.72%，64位元的家用版Windows 7佔了3.67%，32位元的家用版Windows 7佔了2.61%，總計佔了98.35%，而Windows Server 2008 R2則佔了1.52%，Windows 10佔了0.03%，至於Windows XP則因比例太低而未被列入統計圖表中。</span><br />\n<br />\n全文網址：<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F114338&d=LpDakJBiuObdGkynJVcQHb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e2b691a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114338</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static4.ithome.com.tw/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/win7_0_2_0.jpg?itok=sotQgAxY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic4.ithome.com.tw%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Fwin7_0_2_0.jpg%3Fitok%3DsotQgAxY&h=c151ea58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>示意圖，與新聞事件無關。</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">卡巴斯基實驗室（Kaspersky Lab）的全球研究暨分析總監Costin Raiu上周指出，受到WannaCry勒索軟體影響最劇的視窗作業系統為Windows 7，高達98%被感染的電腦為Windows 7作業系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，卡巴斯基實驗室的統計依舊顯示了有Windows 10系統受害，應是利用傳統的惡意電子郵件附件作為感染途徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Malware Tech估計，截至上周五（5/19）全球約有41.7萬台的電腦感染了WannaCry。</span></div>"},{"pid":"d055ee3edbb1871a1fd80db5a6f05c93ea45e495","tid":253861,"uid":79993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:58:02.000Z","msg":"唔講window8有幾多人中?定係大垃圾無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申:window 8.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a15410bc0f3d2ace83802404b920b5857f3275c9","tid":253861,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T22:54:56.000Z","msg":"用 Linux + wine 呢？"},{"pid":"55fd5d925f251791580374d2c396eb6ecb1f4eb3","tid":253861,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用 Linux + wine 呢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f56f48c03f19e98e623a10c6285d383175c5fb6","tid":253861,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">MacOSX呢？</span>"},{"pid":"cc95c31623963cd29e864dc10fb7b68178bb43db","tid":253861,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講window8有幾多人中?定係大垃圾無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申:window 8.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\nWannacry 都唔想理佢"},{"pid":"a535c77b7282e994799016acb70827d5b829effa","tid":253861,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講window8有幾多人中?定係大垃圾無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申:window 8.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\nwannacry見到佢就喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f163d36af027cab0e2b8266ac4fbff97991c24b","tid":253861,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"我知道windows8好戇鳩 但係8.1 係咪一樣都係柒?"}]}